BOOK AWARD

   Apprenti'Bus kids reward author

Learning through entrepreneurship

   A sucessful year for the youth

L DANS LA VILLE AT ROLAND GARROS

   A week-end about tennis

Founded in 1998, Sport dans la Ville is France's leading non-profit, serving
disadvantaged kids through sports and job training.

   IFRAME: https://www.youtube.com/embed/5r7E_JpBZu8

   Our programs are dedicated to serving youth at every stage of their
   development.
   Through free football/soccer and basketball programs, we impart the
   values of self-confidence, teamwork, dedication and hard work, leading
   young people on the path toward a brighter future.

   5,500
   enrolled children in the sport programs

   36
   sport centers in France

   +25%
   increase for LDLV Progam
   See more

Find out about our programs

